<L>__{interior beatrix's house hallway and stable night}
<A>__{columbus and fernando lead the mule into the white washed, stone floored hallway of the modest house. fernando is mute, shocked by what he just witnessed. columbus takes the mule into its stall, and as he does so, his mother, beatrix, appears from the kitchen to greet them. she is a beautiful woman in her twenties, a calm, strong, domestic personality. columbus tousles the boy's hair. fernando glances at his mother but looks subdued and doesn't say anything.}
